Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.04,0:02:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What now, dad...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.58,0:02:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:14.50,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H1E1F1E&\3c&H9A9B86&}I'm going to run a 3 km marathon every morning \NAim for the star of the marathons! {毎朝3キロマラソンやるぜ\Nめざせマラソンの星 - no clue what's this last star bit about, assumed reference to kyojin no hoshi}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.06,0:02:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it that promised to get up every morning \Nand run a marathon with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's Sunday!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.83,0:02:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear any excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't tolerate a man who breaks his promises!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You gutless wreck!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.20,0:02:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You left me running alone! There! {わしだけ走らせおって}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.82,0:02:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks fun! I'll play go chasing one another with you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru! I'll beat some proper grit into you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.98,0:02:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never again let this...
