Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.68,0:02:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Taru...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.31,0:03:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think dad's too harsh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, you brought this upon yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd not get spanked if you kept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That much I can tell you myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have agreed on those weird enterprises! \NBut dad will rough me up again if I quit now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there some magic \Nthat makes things go exactly as you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.88,0:03:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Using this should help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama comes in carrying takoyaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.46,0:03:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought you some takoyaki while I was shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This - True Storing. As you wear it on your neck, \Nit makes your words true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.34,0:03:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru! You don't understand what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:04:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What I need is something that makes things go \Nexactly the way that I judge to be the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.02,0:04:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can use this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Lend me it for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad will take me to a department store today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now realize it! {guess, kinda like jittai - "true state; actual condition; reality"}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, I'm going to the department store. \NYou coming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.09,0:04:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You go or you don't go! \NAnswer immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.02,0:04:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go, I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it quick, I'll wait downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it works! I'm infinitely lucky! {no clue what's this nanmoshi}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.14,0:04:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing! This is an item that gets you anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've shown me \Nsomething so convenient sooner, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.44,0:04:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell is taking you so long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.30,0:04:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Come right now, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:05:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,At the department store, dad buys me anything I like!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll buy you anything you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Jet Bomber! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,PC drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And this... He'll buy me this too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad, Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't stop laughing from this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I made myself literally unable to stop laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My belly hurts from laughing so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.55,0:05:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My magic can't last for more than ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In ten minutes, you lose everything you gained.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And those ten minutes just ran out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.26,0:05:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that to say I'm destined to lose \Nwhatever he buys for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I was getting too happy too fast! {premature joy; short-lived elation}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're happy with all the stuff I bought for you \Ngetting ran over by a car? {せっかくわしが買ってやったものひかれて喜んでいるやつがあるか}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk. As if I never bought it. {unsure}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it, dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This damned item leaves nothing but emptiness in my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My guts rise up against it! {/it irritates me}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru's gu-gu-guts rose up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.16,0:06:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you so happy about, Taru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull back! Pull back, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to see here! There was never anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru was fun to watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Where, exactly? \NI have no more patience for this item!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As can be seen from this food chain...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,At times like this, I like to gaze at Iyona-chan longingly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Both the humans and animals living on this earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course, the plants too, \Nare all a part of a single bigger process,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.84,0:07:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,where they survive through helping one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, if we value the animals and the nature, \Nthat also means we value ourselves and all of the humankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think so too, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually think, isn't it the same between us humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:08:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If we all help each other \Nand reciprocate the attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.66,0:08:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure everyone will become happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Very true, I think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nailed it, Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't really understand a thing though, Taru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.34,0:08:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, Iyona!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I support that too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And what exactly did you understand \Nfrom what she said, Jabao-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.18,0:08:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I got it, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, it takes some guts \Nto be saying corny stuff without any shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Neyo, you jerk! How dare you \Nmake fun of Iyona-chan? Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Honmaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.84,0:08:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I also think, cherishing nature is important, \Nso from now on...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gonna happen from now on, Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.67,0:09:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be grateful for the blessings of nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.15,0:09:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Like not being picky about school lunches \Nand trying to eat everything without leftovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea, Honmaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.34,0:09:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He sure is aiming high!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But will he really live up to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.77,0:09:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They put in my most hated bell pepper!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, what are you hesitating about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.75,0:09:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't eat it soon, \Ngym class will start without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.79,0:09:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, what's the matter, Honmaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I know exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It has that bell pepper you hate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose you're gonna leave your school lunch behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.83,0:10:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey-hey-hey, check this out, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Determined to put a stake in the ground earlier, \NHonmaru is gonna leave behind his meal now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean to say \Neverything Ijigawa-san said was true, Honmaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat it, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.06,0:10:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, be so kind as to answer \Nfor your own claims, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't you a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A while ago, when I overate bell peppers, \NI was vomiting severely and fell ill with a fever! {no clue what's this harakowashite part; was "ゲロはいて" in manga} {/my stomach went bust }
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when I came to hate them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you leave behind even a single pod, \NI ain't letting it slide!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You get it now? {guess, wakaru?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you do that for, Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, this is yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.82,0:11:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, alright? \NIt's the best thing ever! {not sure what he means}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.61,0:11:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it look tasty? \NAlright, let's get full!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Upon a closer look, \Nthese bell peppers really look quite yummy! Peppers! {memeing until marty tells me off}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's yummy! I'm telling the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure to leave nothing on your plate, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.91,0:11:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wearing True Storing. But when...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see, Taru! When you pretended to strangle me earlier, \Nyou were actually putting this on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.59,0:12:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, as long as you restrain yourself while using it, \Nthis might actually be a fantastic item!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I just had a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.37,0:12:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Friggin' good! Harako playfully vaulted ten at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.54,0:12:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Some vaulting boxes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, the winner of the World Junior Gymnastics \NChampionship, it's like taking candy from a baby. {to take candy from a baby; to accomplish something with ease; to twist a baby's arm​}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.34,0:12:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're boasting about it so proudly, \Nyou're still a long way off, Harako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say, Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And how good are you \Nto be talking like that, Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you clearly, when I playfully vault \Nover 80 boxes at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Vault, vault!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,For starters, we haven't got that many vaulting boxes \Nin all of our school. Right, Jabao-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.62,0:13:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what's that thing over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I'm seeing it for the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, people! Don't be too surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, hold up. If they're not surprised at all, it'll be a bummer. {/boring}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,People, prepare to be surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,For this Edojo Honmaru is going to vault over those 80 boxes \Nand land safely before your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A fool's errand. You'll smash right into your big mouth. {to talk through one's hat; to blow one's own horn - not sure what me means by "you'll stay withing limits of your boating"}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.91,0:13:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.25,0:13:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:14:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch this, Iyona-chan. I'm becoming a hero now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.04,0:14:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! He actually vaulted over it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.10,0:14:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! If Honmaru can do something, \Nthere's no reason I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.81,0:14:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Atomic Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There can only be one hero in this class!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no... Catch it! {guess, no clue what's this krakken, not in manga; TLC?}{Episode 42:\N14:36: I'm hearing "くらっけ" for that last part.\NI'm not even sure if it's a word.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.05,0:14:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?! World's #1 nails, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought, no ordinary human can do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it sure feels good to finally be a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:15:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,When ten minutes pass and magic wears off, True Storing \Nexchanges good things happened to you for bad things. {/makes bad things happen to you for every good thing happened}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You should've said so sooner, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.03,0:15:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Honmaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru hurt his leg while vaulting 80 boxes at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? What? Vaulting over 80 boxes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan forgot it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes people forget it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Like about the department store yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.42,0:15:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a devastating item after all! {same, "empty"}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought I'd leave my mark \Nbefore Iyona-chan's eyes today...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you can't rely on Taru's magic for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It only lasts ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Niruru, let's play with this True Storing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.40,0:15:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Putting it on Honmaru's papa should be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hold back with that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't risk angering dad, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.29,0:16:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Board-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Body disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I too late, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How was work today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.31,0:16:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. I had to make a round on publishing houses, \Nbeen walking all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My legs are wood-stiff. {/became sticks}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.75,0:16:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just my imagination. \NIt was nothing, right? {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm starving, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:16:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is dinner coming soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure. Almost ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell is tantalizing. \NIt draws my nose out. {no clue what he said or meant originally}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that just now...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.70,0:17:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't it delicious, dad? Mom's cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru's mama cooking genius today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.38,0:17:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true. Makes my cheeks fall off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, Honmaru, is this your doing again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No clue...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see you're lying. \NIt's written on your faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.44,0:18:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Honmaru's papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard it so many times by now, \NI have parasites living in my ears! {I gave up}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything I say becomes reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Honmaru's papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.86,0:18:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't this a powerful item, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say it out loud. \NClearly, everyone would want such a powerful item.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta be careful and consider well what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.52,0:18:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The walls have ears and the doors have eyes, they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.94,0:18:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So many popped up! Papa amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to put in more thought when using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:19:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What would be my wish if I were Honmaru's papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just ask it for whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.09,0:19:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How about money, dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.21,0:19:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Cloven-hoofed idiots!
