Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.51,0:19:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I'd seriously wish for something that petty?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd sooner boil some tea with my bare hands. {to split one's sides laughing; to be convulsed with laughter; to boil tea with one's navel (using the heat generated by laughing)​}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What an annoying item! {guess, was "うっとーし" in manga; TLC?}{19:24: I'm hearing "いちちゅっとうしいな"\NI'm not sure about the first part but I can definitely make out "鬱陶しい" in the second part.\NEither he's so irate that he's flubbing his words or he could be saying "一々" in the first part.\NThat might be a bit of a stretch though.\NI think what you have now is fine.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey-hey, dad, say it sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.21,0:19:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, if I can wish for anything at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.91,0:19:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, now say it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite hard to come up with something \Nwhen you're demanding it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we first ask your mom to use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Honmaru's mama using it too! {/I don't mind ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:19:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? It makes anything you say true?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.11,0:20:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything is fine. \NJust say whatever you want to come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What does Honmaru's mama think? {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.00,0:20:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I can't just say it on the spur. \NIt'll become a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom weighing her wish so seriously. \NI'd hate to bring bad news to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But even if her wish comes true, \Nten minutes later Taru's magic will wear off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And everything will become nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.82,0:20:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help but pity her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. With warmth in our hearts,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,our family becomes eternally happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.39,0:21:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, and then, with peace and harmony,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,we become a family that's always on good terms, \Nlaughing endlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true! I feel so much warmer and happier!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.30,0:21:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, I wish it'd stay like this forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.09,0:21:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But before you know it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.75,0:21:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Huh? But ten minutes ran out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.82,0:21:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.81,0:21:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, the magic of happiness is a lasting one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.98,0:22:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic of happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.73,0:22:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.08,0:22:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, Taru! My belly hurts from laughing this much!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, endure! Endure!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.26,0:22:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right! My tum-tum hurts too now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.98,0:22:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, yay! It's a pool, a pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.02,0:22:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, let's swim, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.75,0:22:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... Wait a minute there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.11,0:22:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru... Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.89,0:22:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Honmaru can't stop ogling at Iyona in her swimsuit! {to have a lewd look on one's face; to ogle​}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.70,0:22:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.35,0:22:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.05,0:22:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Magical Taruruuto-kun:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.75,0:23:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Summer! The Pool is Open.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.42,0:23:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, your eyes are a little naughty.
